Standard capabilities
Addr. ID
----------------
0040  0D = PCI Bridge Subsystem ID
0060  05 = Message Signaled Interrupts, MSI
0090  10 = PCI Express
00E0  01 = PCI Power management

Standard capabilities
Addr. ID
----------------

0060  05 = Message Signaled Interrupts, MSI

00E0  01 = PCI Power management

Standard capabilities
Addr. ID
----------------
0040  01 = PCI Power management
0050  05 = Message Signaled Interrupts, MSI
0070  11 = MSI-X
00A0  10 = PCI Express

Extended capabilities
Addr. ID
----------------
0100  0001 = Advanced Error Reporting, AER
0150  000E = Alternative Routing ID Interpretation, ARI
0160  0010 = Single Root IO Virtualization, SR-IOV
01D0  000D = Access Control Services, ACS

Bus = 01  Device = 00  Function = 01
Vendor = 8086 = Intel Corporation
Device = 1528 = Ethernet Controller 10-Gigabit X540-AT2
SubVendor = 15D9 = Super Micro Computer Inc
SubDevice = 1528 = ?

Standard capabilities
Addr. ID
----------------
0040  01 = PCI Power management
0050  05 = Message Signaled Interrupts, MSI
0070  11 = MSI-X
00A0  10 = PCI Express

Extended capabilities
Addr. ID
----------------
0100  0001 = Advanced Error Reporting, AER
0150  000E = Alternative Routing ID Interpretation, ARI
0160  0010 = Single Root IO Virtualization, SR-IOV
01D0  000D = Access Control Services, ACS

Vendor = 1C58 = HGST, Inc.
Device = 0003 = Ultrastar SN100 Series NVMe SSD
SubVendor = 1C58 = HGST, Inc.
SubDevice = 0003 = Ultrastar SN100/SN150 NVMe SSD

Standard capabilities
Addr. ID
----------------
00C0  01 = PCI Power management
0070  10 = PCI Express
00C8  05 = Message Signaled Interrupts, MSI
00E0  11 = MSI-X

Standard capabilities
Addr. ID
----------------
0040  0D = PCI Bridge Subsystem ID
0060  05 = Message Signaled Interrupts, MSI
0090  10 = PCI Express
00E0  01 = PCI Power management

Standard capabilities
Addr. ID
----------------
0050  01 = PCI Power management
0068  10 = PCI Express
00A8  05 = Message Signaled Interrupts, MSI
00C0  11 = MSI-X

0148  000E = Alternative Routing ID Interpretation, ARI
